    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nKeyboard doesn't automatically opens up when you open any listed options in DeckOptions. You have to tap on the empty edit text to bring the keyboard up.  \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40427461/164933747-493ad4ac-c3ee-4f2b-bd06-42a9da8b9316.mp4\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nNot sure but extending DeckOptions to PreferenceFragmentCompat and then overriding onResume() method like mentioned here : https://stackoverflow.com/a/59677185/9062752\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nInstead of EditTextPreferences we can create Dialogs for different options and can call the displayKeyboard() function like here #10593\r\n\r\n",
